response.activities: Welcome to my space. My name is Mattias Lindblom. Artist, songwriter/producer from Stockholm, Sweden. I'm 50% of Vacuum. Feel free to surf www.vacuum-people.com or one of the amazing fansites around the net (www.vacuum-music.com, www.vacuum-global etc...just google). Also, there's www.myspace.com/vacuumpeople or iTunes for sound. My first love in life is music. Through music I see beautiful places, meet amazing people and audiences, work with some of the best songwriters, artists around so needless to say, I feel quite blessed. So what can You tell me? Drop me a line. Stay holy, loving, inspired, forgiving, creative, kind, honest, faithful, and believing.
